name: You Will Take Me To Jabba Now (V)
Text: 'When you play this Interrupt, may place a Rep stacked on your Objective in Used Pile. May deploy Seeking An Audience or an alien to Audience Chamber (for -1 Force) from Reserve Deck; reshuffle. OR Reveal up to 3 Aliens stacked on I Know That Laugh or from hand (X = number of aliens revealed); activate X Force.',
